# 🔐 Secure Vulnerability Scanner

A lightweight penetration testing tool inspired by OWASP ZAP. Scans a given URL for missing security headers, vulnerable forms, and common misconfigurations.

## 🔧 Features
- Checks HTTP response code
- Validates key security headers
- Detects common vulnerability patterns
- Extracts HTML forms
- Performs basic port scan on server

## ▶️ How to Run
```bash
pip install -r requirements.txt
python scanner.py
